CPAN-Checksums-Signature version 0.01
=====================================

Proposal for verifying CHECKSUMS distributed on CPAN.

Supports signature verifcation via GnuPG v1, GnuPG v2 or Crypt::OpenPGP. This
module contains the PAUSE PGP signing key for trust. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

